S H A R E  T H E  W E I G H T
Constant monitoring of Covid 19 through news updates and social media feeds intensify feelings of worry and distress. Self-care in the wake of the coronavirus outbreak is the primary goal thus we at flirtatious would like to focus on mental and physical health . Staying fit can keep you healthy physically, but exercise also boosts your mental and spiritual health, too. Thus we here start a circuit of “ FLEX WITH FLIRTATIOUS “, a good workout can simply make your outlook brighter during a global pandemic.. Thanks to the great talented bunch here to Help You Stay Healthy by an insight into their work out routines.  Stronger together! 
Show us your favourite flex !
